               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17901027-62-cd337" type="crimeDate">5th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901027-62-off336 t17901027-62-cd337"></join>, fifteen yards of woollen cloth, value 10 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17901027-62-victim721" type="victimName">
                           Arthur Skier 
                           Lofty
                        <interp inst="t17901027-62-victim721" type="surname" value="Lofty"></interp>
